    "description": "<strong>CHERNOGRAD Demo</strong> is a story-driven simulation game. In the demo version, you will play Day 0 and Day 1 from the main game.<br><br>The player has to take on the role of an employee of the Citizen's Tranquility Agency and keep an eye on the residents of the 15th district of Chernograd. Each flat is equipped with an activity tracking system, and if it notices a violation by a citizen, a video and audio recorder will allow you to connect to the house and flat to find the offender, make a report and send it to the Truth Finder along with the rest of the evidence.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/c500477300c3e96ad878cdbf29f8befc.poster.avif?t=1728924715\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/c500477300c3e96ad878cdbf29f8befc.webm?t=1728924715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/c500477300c3e96ad878cdbf29f8befc.mp4?t=1728924715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Surveillance of citizen's flats, using specialised equipment<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/3ff31cfba3a68cf4d5ba6dbe0d0357bb.poster.avif?t=1728924715\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/3ff31cfba3a68cf4d5ba6dbe0d0357bb.webm?t=1728924715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/3ff31cfba3a68cf4d5ba6dbe0d0357bb.mp4?t=1728924715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Making reports on violations that affect the fate of citizens and the entire country<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/9026e34a0fa0c32d31a7bdea3603db39.poster.avif?t=1728924715\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/9026e34a0fa0c32d31a7bdea3603db39.webm?t=1728924715\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3159370/extras/9026e34a0fa0c32d31a7bdea3603db39.mp4?t=1728924715\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
